by Goatboy on Tue May 04, 2010 4:18 pm	([msg=38352]see Re: Mind control through mass media???[/msg])
I was thinking about this thread while I was driving, and I remembered something from when I was younger. Probably age 10-11, just going from elementary to middle school. I recall thinking to myself "I don't really know about all the popular celebrities. I'm not too well-informed."How backwards I was! I felt left out of the loop because I didn't know who Tom Cruise was dating or because I didn't know the lyrics to the latest Aaron Carter song. Looking back on that now, I'm glad I wasn't indoctrinated by Hollywood.
